307
00:20:27.541 --> 00:20:30.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Let's talk about what<i> you </i>would like.

308
00:20:32.500 --> 00:20:35.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Shoes.
-[laughs]

309
00:20:35.375 --> 00:20:38.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Fair. Did the apple
buy me another question?

310
00:20:40.875 --> 00:20:41.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why not?

311
00:20:42.666 --> 00:20:44.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
