312
00:20:45.291 --> 00:20:47.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
What was Dracula
going to give you?

313
00:20:48.666 --> 00:20:51.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
