314
00:20:51.625 --> 00:20:54.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You were helping build an army
for Dracula.

315
00:20:54.500 --> 00:20:56.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You were advising him.

316
00:20:56.458 --> 00:20:58.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
He was going to kill
all the humans--

317
00:20:58.666 --> 00:20:59.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I didn't know that.

318
00:21:00.416 --> 00:21:02.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I didn't understand that until later.

319
00:21:03.666 --> 00:21:05.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
