343
00:22:14.333 --> 00:22:15.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I believed in his work.

344
00:22:15.666 --> 00:22:18.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
But obviously
you expected something.

345
00:22:18.541 --> 00:22:21.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Even if that was only to be spared
