346
00:22:22.291 --> 00:22:25.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Or to be kept in a cage.
[laughs]

347
00:22:25.166 --> 00:22:26.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
So that worked out well.

348
00:22:28.000 --> 00:22:30.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-[chuckling]
-Seriously.

349
00:22:30.833 --> 00:22:32.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Other than shoes.

350
00:22:33.541 --> 00:22:35.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, this isn't
a serious conversation.

351
00:22:35.791 --> 00:22:37.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
