357
00:22:52.333 --> 00:22:53.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Much the same.

358
00:22:54.083 --> 00:22:55.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
