372
00:23:32.125 --> 00:23:33.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hm.

373
00:23:35.916 --> 00:23:37.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
