375
00:23:41.375 --> 00:23:44.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Even though he'd decided to kill
every human being on Earth

376
00:23:44.458 --> 00:23:46.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
because they murdered his wife.

377
00:23:46.541 --> 00:23:49.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I'm sure you would have been
the only survivor of the human race.

378
00:23:49.875 --> 00:23:51.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Makes perfect sense.

379
00:23:52.000 --> 00:23:54.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
On the bright side,
after everybody on Earth was dead,

380
00:23:54.958 --> 00:23:57.333 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
