387
00:24:15.416 --> 00:24:19.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
In commerce, we don't have
to have faith in each other, do we?

388
00:24:19.166 --> 00:24:20.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
