389
00:24:20.875 --> 00:24:23.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's simple.
There are rules.

390
00:24:24.000 --> 00:24:25.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I give you something,

391
00:24:25.708 --> 00:24:27.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
you give me something.

392
00:24:36.125 --> 00:24:38.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You understand that when
I forge a night creature,

393
00:24:38.375 --> 00:24:40.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
they are bound to my command.

394
00:24:40.666 --> 00:24:42.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Their loyalty is to me.

395
00:24:42.541 --> 00:24:44.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Well, maybe we'll talk
about that another time.

396
00:24:44.458 --> 00:24:47.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Until then... I'll get you some shoes.

397
00:24:48.416 --> 00:24:50.041 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
