400
00:24:55.416 --> 00:24:56.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
About?

401
00:24:56.666 --> 00:24:58.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Whatever you like.

402
00:24:59.041 --> 00:25:01.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
