Beaten down a dozen different ways,

405
00:25:06.208 --> 00:25:07.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
and you don't give up on yourself.

406
00:25:08.625 --> 00:25:10.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's... nice.

407
00:25:13.041 --> 00:25:14.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[footsteps recede]

408
00:25:20.916 --> 00:25:22.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
