416
00:26:41.208 --> 00:26:44.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Get back on your ship,
with your monstrosities, and leave.

417
00:26:46.625 --> 00:26:49.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It seems my ship has already left.

418
00:26:50.791 --> 00:26:52.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It has a shrewd captain.

419
00:26:53.000 --> 00:26:56.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
