that I'd stopped praying.

420
00:26:56.791 --> 00:26:58.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Can you imagine that?

421
00:26:59.375 --> 00:27:03.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I stopped praying and devoting myself,
and I hadn't even noticed.

422
00:27:04.666 --> 00:27:07.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
What a monster I have become.

423
00:27:08.250 --> 00:27:12.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You don't want me to be a monster
right here in your nice port, do you?

424
00:27:13.916 --> 00:27:15.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Let us pass.

425
00:27:16.416 --> 00:27:17.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
No.

426
00:27:18.000 --> 00:27:21.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
My ship is gone,
