427
00:27:22.541 --> 00:27:24.250 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Let us through.

428
00:27:24.333 --> 00:27:28.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We'll drive you and your filthy creatures
into the sea if we have to.

429
00:27:28.291 --> 00:27:30.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We know what's been
happening in Wallachia.

430
00:27:30.666 --> 00:27:32.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It will<i> not </i>happen here.

431
00:27:33.750 --> 00:27:35.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
