432
00:27:36.041 --> 00:27:39.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I cannot believe
this is happening again.

433
00:27:40.625 --> 00:27:42.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It's absurd.

434
00:27:42.416 --> 00:27:45.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I just... can't.

435
00:27:45.916 --> 00:27:48.791 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Why do I keep doing the same thing

436
00:27:48.875 --> 00:27:51.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
