437
00:27:51.666 --> 00:27:54.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Isn't that the definition of insanity?

438
00:27:55.125 --> 00:27:56.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Am I mad?

439
00:27:57.750 --> 00:27:59.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[growling]

440
00:27:59.291 --> 00:28:01.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You know... one day,

441
00:28:01.375 --> 00:28:04.375 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
the last one of you will ask me,

442
00:28:04.458 --> 00:28:09.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
"Why did you work with Dracula himself
to murder all the people?"

443
00:28:10.166 --> 00:28:12.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
And do you know what I'll say?

444
00:28:13.250 --> 00:28:16.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
It's because you're all
so fucking rude. [snaps fingers]

445
00:28:19.375 --> 00:28:21.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[growling, snarling]

446
00:28:23.291 --> 00:28:25.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[men screaming]

447
00:28:26.916 --> 00:28:28.875 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bring me fresh material!

448
00:28:38.583 --> 00:28:40.750 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[men yelling, screaming]

449
00:28:47.166 --> 00:28:48.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
[roars]

450
00:28:52.916 --> 00:28:54.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
